nter; font-size: 22px; margin: 0;"&gt; “金融机构可能需要在融资增长和保持融资减排步伐&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/u9QT1mgrY_BaVLHRmpuAjnH8-jVjKSvajuxykKqR8YZ8Sz3rke634UUcBTQZQ6_HzFilD4uRW4hTAXyqOv5lXiAGAGx2Kfn6xPQNcrU-5yLs-QBoXtYbnofHomKbnxx3VMLrTy8wRuPUEUBbpNjeoMgnPPBuxS8XhrCu9dEaxo4VO9E08BwDzXnHCIlMA3PuO-v8DE2fn0YCX2YD0rxPo-htgDrYy3KRdTkrDszzQTtwVit1OscKgZb3gBkAUZQCmfJVIhsPa5hSeP5vikCZSw5v0_RucQccX2L8Zrdep7vxGDsn6sR242yI-E6cn8dovwcNWDJfklqI3W8afhpvIBt3WtlI27X2ns1L-7mxFQ2envjXH235c85TQzKsU04eezhdXblveREmL-cH-nSNmVN_-pXXbTI_N13xN-Ivo6HlpovRKd-RPT3yRj8XckV29UAWNVX7c2NTv1s_wu27CzcT4HTsUrGxTjbJ77GPwV6VgGTphnRSRgsoUCljhmyVcXSXapWHz31LkKhVsI-DFdxz6qBf4xI3ZUkLSUs-IUSjmgJyNuQ5SNq4/Yt1YW145U757yuCEG0Y5kaCEi_qQPcZ6/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: inherit;" target="_blank" title="巴克莱表示，不同的气候政策正在迫使人们进行权衡"&gt;之间做出选择&lt;/a&gt;”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-weight: 700; margin: 8px 0 0;"&gt;巴克莱银行&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; line-height: 140%; margin: 8px 0 0;"&gt;巴克莱银行在今年早些时候的一份报告中表示，主要经济体在如何实现能源转型方面存在巨大分歧，有可能迫使银行做出艰难的选择。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt; “这没有先例”&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;作者： &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2XymKUN9_9KFIIe0lT7DWnWYU9HlFcV3EZngOEsjMU4NDspi0MYDov-IiJmwRYYh7-dFYPiC9BvYV8xvfH12o83zAP6PnxyfpVPfqBsd1VzVEHKemVEtoWaUqo5_f_iqGAJGrT91mc2g89bbaadKtGUeyJj6BaZLL4AVBZy3dVHF-vZsMqA-y7In1ycrIN1cxsSsFBVh-2YHKcOFn71e_AH52VvF5oNH_92NbvGWraluetkPvjJ0xGUmky3uW19_ErFlC6ifTKKIoaVAbXilwZRQElnipQQ-KcpkbzMeMR5F6V1U6Uec00W42ByiGF1x-bNoFklae72DXk3h69B2FRkS0ojeQuc_FbtIS7T58LeYPXoGVqQs39Iumbmc1c9FpIKhY0WYdpVNBzxLtypX1S6GR2wk7H0-FBOq61b_Ba0VU_9H4gELknM3NKBhYcPa8CeXte5rf-ZWGKUIpP_bHAubS6F-Hg1jAFzAUQLtghrDokXW_w/WJWZO76i_PTWT4zIKdKF6UJWzL11KsY4/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="奥利维亚·雷蒙